title: FL Studio 12 BETA
description:
Welcome to the FL Studio 11.5.13 Beta (this *is* FL Studio 12 in development, there will be no FL Studio 11.5...

This beta WILL expire on - January 15 2015...

The beta includes FL Studio 32 and 64 Bit - You can install one or both using the installer options. You see new 'FL Studio 11.5 (beta)' and 'FL Studio 11.5 (beta) (64bit)' icons.


KNOWN ISSUES

* Harmor image resynthesis crash & image repaint issues
* Check if Options > General > GUI input > Optimize for - has defaulted to the correct setup for your system 
* Select 'Show available' in 32 Bit and open 64 Bit. RAM meter may show 124317500 MB :) not a bug is true.
* Patcher still needs a lot of work for FL12. It will be better in the next Beta.
* FL Studio 64 Bit Shift+Enter = Crash (when Playlist is in focus)
